					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">On request, I slightly reduced the purple tinge that shows up on Protoman in the intro of Mega Man 5. While the intended look was meant to have a purple tinge, many TVs have trouble interpreting it, and so most people remember seeing those colors in a more blue hue. The same entries also show up in Metroid quite a bit, so it was the best compromise between 'intended' and 'what people remember'. <br /><br />The file has been uploaded to the same link.</div>

